      "writtenOn": "2019-09-26T23:04:06Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Makes sense. IIUC the main randomness this is avoiding is the order in which results get appended to ret. We could sort by iteration and then name, or by name and then iteration. Would the latter be more useful? It would require tracking the iteration additionally, however. Also, even if we decide something different, it doesn\u0027t have to be in this CL.",
